    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >[演示版公告]</h2> 你好！<br>我们很高兴地宣布，Skeldungeon 的演示版现已免费提供！<br>在此演示版中，您可以体验总共3个主要关卡。 <br>我们非常感谢您的支持，帮助我们宣传和鼓励，<br>以便更多玩家在尝试演示版后能享受完整版！<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >[实时战略防御]</h2>《骷髅地下城》是一款实时战略防御游戏。控制骷髅设置陷阱，并亲自击败入侵的英雄。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >[设置陷阱]</h2>在夜晚，你可以管理地下城。<br>将陷阱放置在英雄可能入侵的地方，以准备迎接他们的攻击。<br>设置和升级陷阱房间，扩展你的地下城。<br>发现各种神器，找到具有新效果的隐藏组合房间。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3173770/extras/32997de0307cbd16ce910ac262b61f2d.poster.avif?t=1729549692\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3173770/extras/32997de0307cbd16ce910ac262b61f2d.webm?t=1729549692\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3173770/extras/32997de0307cbd16ce910ac262b61f2d.mp4?t=1729549692\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >[骷髅的变身与战斗]</h2>白天，你必须控制骷髅直接参与与来袭英雄的战斗。<br>夺取英雄的头颅，使用他们的能力。<br>根据情况使用剑、魔法、盾牌和飞镖等各种变身，以有效地击败英雄。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3173770/extras/54a9ae536b61c6465fdd6526aafd2d36.poster.avif?t=1729549692\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3173770/extras/54a9ae536b61c6465fdd6526aafd2d36.webm?t=1729549692\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3173770/extras/54a9ae536b61c6465fdd6526aafd2d36.mp4?t=1729549692\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >[关卡与无尽模式]</h2>面对越来越强大的英雄，完成所有七个关卡。<br>通过随机波次和效果的无尽模式获得高分。<br>在完成关卡和无尽模式后，获得更高的分数以与其他玩家竞争排名。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3173770/extras/2e215a3b5956bac407065e53294eeb0c.poster.avif?t=1729549692\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3173770/extras/2e215a3b5956bac407065e53294eeb0c.webm?t=1729549692\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3173770/extras/2e215a3b5956bac407065e53294eeb0c.mp4?t=1729549692\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >[重复游戏]</h2>你不能一次性复活魔王，要不断牺牲英雄。<br>使用完成关卡后获得的特性点来增强陷阱和骷髅，创建你自己的构建。<br>解锁新的陷阱房间、变身和皮肤，并进行游戏。通过特性和改造来自由调整难度，获得额外分数。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3173770/extras/cc0360e65ce90fae679d9ac69191fe6d.poster.avif?t=1729549692\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3173770/extras/cc0360e65ce90fae679d9ac69191fe6d.webm?t=1729549692\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3173770/extras/cc0360e65ce90fae679d9ac69191fe6d.mp4?t=1729549692\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
